UnsupportedKeySizeException - Exception in psi.exception
This exception is thrown whenever the server attempts to initialize a session with an unsupported key size, or when a client attempts to load a session associated to an unsupported key size.
UnsupportedKeySizeException(PsiAlgorithm, int) - Constructor for exception psi.exception.UnsupportedKeySizeException
 
UnsupportedKeySizeRuntimeException - Exception in psi.exception
This exception is thrown whenever the UnsupportedKeySize exception is not generated by an external input (e.g, sent by the client) but due to internal errors.
UnsupportedKeySizeRuntimeException(PsiAlgorithm, int) - Constructor for exception psi.exception.UnsupportedKeySizeRuntimeException
